kotha janta ( telugu : కొత్త జంట , english : new pair ) is a telugu film directed by maruthi and produced by bunny vasu on the prestigious geetha arts banner . it stars allu sirish and regina cassandra in the lead roles . the film released on 1 may 2014 to mixed reviews from critics but positive response from the movie viewers due to its high comedy content . the film was a commercial hit .